<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>68</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 8
 rén liú zhōng jí cōng cōng, jí cōng cōng, nǐ lái wǒ wǎng nán běi xī dōng.
 měi rén de xīn zhōng, dōu yǒu yī běn jīng, suān tián kǔ là shì rén shēng.
 yī shēng zhōng yǒu duō shǎo xǐ hé yōu yī shēng zhōng yǒu duō shǎo shī bài hé chéng gōng?
 tiān xià rén rén dōu shì yī gè yàng, dào lù bù shì yī lù shùn fēng.
 yī tiān de nán chù yī tiān dāng, yī tiān yào zuò hǎo yī tiān de shì qíng,
 kào zhe shén yǒng gǎn de miàn duì shēng huó nì jìng yě huì biàn shùn jìng.
 lù jiù zài nǐ de jiǎo xià, chōng mǎn xìn xīn qù zǒu,
 yī bù yī gè xīn tái jiē, rén shēng zhī lù gèng jiā guāng míng.</lyrics>
<title>rén shēng 迦南68</title>
</song>